Comprehensive biochemistry: albumin 30.6 g/L, ALT 9.0 U/L, AST 26.7 U/L, potassium 3.8 mmol/L, sodium 136 mmol/L, creatinine 66.5 μmol/L, glucose 5.64 mmol/L, creatine kinase 111.0 U/L, CK-MB 15.1 U/L, total cholesterol 4.17 mmol/L, triglycerides 0.60 mmol/L, LDL 2.47 mmol/L;  
